---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact"
  description="Contacteaza echipa Balador.ro pentru intrebari, sugestii sau colaborari."
>
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container-main">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-8 text-center">Contact</h1>

        <div class="card p-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-400 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-primary-950" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Trimite-ne un Email</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">Suntem aici sa te ajutam cu orice intrebare sau sugestie.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-3">Scrie-ne la adresa:</p>
            <a
              href="mailto:contact@andrad.ro"
              class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-700 hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors"
            >
              contact@andrad.ro
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Pentru ce ne poti contacta:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Intrebari despre recenziile sau articolele noastre</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Sugestii de produse pentru recenzii viitoare</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Corectii sau actualizari ale informatiilor</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Propuneri de colaborare</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-accent-50 rounded-lg border border-accent-200">
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-800 text-center">
              <strong>Timp de raspuns:</strong> Incercam sa raspundem la toate mesajele in maxim 48 de ore lucratoare.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
